title: Royal Selangor Club cancels booking, Zaid claims political pressure
text:
The Royal Selangor Club has allegedly cancelled a booking by former de facto law minister Zaid Ibrahim, where it was speculated he would announce his decision to join DAP. 
Speaking to Malaysiakini , Zaid believes the decision was due to political pressure.
